Pocket Amsterdam
Public transit routes for Amsterdam
Hello!
View all the public transit routes and the available stops in Amsterdam on an Interactive map - available for both iPhone and iPad
Features
You can also favorite frequently used routes on both iPhone and iPad
View list of each stops and all modes of transport available from them
Includes data from GVB & CXX public transit agencies
Privacy Policy
We use Google Analytics to understand from which countries the app is used and for how long. This information in an aggregated form is used to identify areas of improvement for our users.
No personally identifiable information is collected.
